column5: Anyone from here drive the van on brucedale and east 26 or 25th with the OFC sticker on the back window?
Yeah...I can tell you who it is.
I saw that van in that area this past June.I think I saw it at Lakair a few years ago.He must get around.
Oh, now I gotta cruise by there to see... I'm just up past Rymal and Sherman...
the hood gangsters better look out...once you guys get your fishing gang formed
You have to have a gold membership
An' thats why you'll never get one......bwah hah ha ha ha
There is this ugly ballerina in a tu tu that gives them out at OFC GTG's.Thats where I got mine at least. Joe
talk about deflation ....first time i lost a tooth i received a nickle...second time a dime ...third time a quarter...you know the times are tough when the fairy hands out a sticker...
I never gotmy sticker ...but I just leave my OFC cap in the rear window .... I find it keeps the hoodlums away
